## **📈 Growth Strategy - Becoming a High-Impact Engineer**

✅ **1. Build Strong Foundations** – Learn **fundamentals** in **Data Structures & Algorithms**, **Computer Architecture**, and **Version Control (Git)**.  
✅ **2. Develop a Specialization** – Master a field **aligned with your strengths** and interests (**AI, Cybersecurity, Cloud, DevOps**).  
✅ **3. Work on Projects** – Apply knowledge in **real-world coding projects** (e.g., Open Source, AI research, Web Apps).  
✅ **4. Build a Portfolio** – Showcase skills on **GitHub, Kaggle (for ML), or personal blogs**.  
✅ **5. Get Certified** – Industry-recognized certifications (**IBM AI Cert, AWS Solutions Architect, OSCP (Cybersecurity)**) enhance credibility.

